{"tid":1800572,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"罷韓正妹蛻變成「健美女神」，勇奪IFBB冠軍","createTime":"2019-12-28T03:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T03:13:23.000Z","uid":215823,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0badd6f96cafdcca97acb46c2b613185e8290f","tid":1800572,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"台中蔡姓正妹在今年7月6日因在高雄市香蕉煎餅店廣德家與韓粉起衝突，從此在網路上慘遭韓粉霸凌圍勦。如今事過境遷，蔡姓正妹不因此事被擊倒，反而在近日職業健美比賽勇奪冠軍，蔡姓正妹也發文說「認真覺得我18歲的人生好精彩」。<br />\n<br />\n蔡姓女學生透露，在10月底開始準備職業健美賽，只花了2個月準備就拿到人生第一場比賽冠軍，「真的超級感動，辛苦都值得了，覺得人生真的充滿驚喜！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ps9d4Fr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fps9d4Fr.jpg&h=f38730da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vssSAM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvssSAM7.jpg&h=230866ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TP6PC0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTP6PC0s.jpg&h=985a63ed&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}